  "text": "Studies previously hypothesized that DKK1 was involved in the downstream targeting of β-catenin/T-cell factor and participated in a negative feedback loop within the Wnt signaling pathway of colon cancer cells [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . In addition, studies revealed that the overexpression of DKK1 was associated with poor patient prognosis [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] , whereas no clear evidence regarding the function of DKK1 in NSCLC was identified.",
